<center><font size=7><b>Dan Dare 1: Pilot Of The Future</b></font></center>
<center>Number of entries found: 4</center><p>
<center>
<table width=600>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Multiface pokes</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD><table border="0">
<tr>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>DESCRIPTION</B></U></TD>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>POKE(s)</B></U></TD>
</TR>
<tr><td>Infinite Energy</td><td>47732,201</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite Ammo</td><td>43544,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite Time</td><td>60677,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>No Treens</td><td>61840.0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Fall Any Height</td><td>42870,24</td></tr>
<tr><td>No Jail Level 3</td><td>42110,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Immunity</td><td>56382,201</td></tr>
</table>
<BR><BR>There is a weird glitch in my copy (only?) of this game. When you face left,
and fire while standing, you sometimes turn into a shot treen!
<BR>
This happens with and without the POKE. I have only tried it on ZXAM 2.0B&nbsp;though...<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>(Gerard Sweeney in Hack Attack III)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Type-in hacks</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>This can be found in <a href="ftp://ftp.void.jump.org/pub/sinclair/magazines/SinclairUser/Issue74/Tape/">this issue of Poke City</a>.
 <i>(Cover Tape in Sinclair User issue 74)</i> 

<br><hr>
This can be found in <a href="ftp://ftp.void.jump.org/pub/sinclair/magazines/YourSinclair/Issue40/Tape/">this issue of Pokes</a> in the alphabetical section.
 <i>(Cover Tape in Your Sinclair issue 40)</i> 

<br><hr>
Original Virgin release:<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<pre>
 10 REM CLEAR 25999
 20 LET T=0: FOR N=64000 TO 64026: READ A: POKE N,A: LET T=T+A: NEXT N
 30 IF T<>2539 THEN PRINT "DATA ERROR": STOP
 40 FOR N=N TO lE9: READ A<256 THEN POKE N,A: NEXT N
 50 RANDOMIZE USR 64000
 60 DATA 221,33,203,92,17,9,3,175,214,1,205,86,5
 70 DATA 48,241,33,27,250,34,133,93,1,17,93,195,17,93,175
 80 DATA 50,6,170: REM INFINITE BULLETS
 90 DATA 50,39,183: REM INFINITE TIME
100 DATA 62,201,50,94,186: REM INFINITE ENERGY
110 DATA 62,201,50,125,173: REM NO ROOF & FLOOR GUNS
120 DATA 195,192,93,999: REM END MARKER
</pre><br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mastertronic re-release:<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<pre>
10 CLEAR 25599
20 LOAD ""SCREEN$
30 LOAD ""CODE
40 POKE 47732,201
50 POKE 43544,0 : REM Infinite ammo
60 POKE 46913,0 : REM Infinite time
70 POKE 42870,24 : REM fall any height
80 POKE 42111,0 : REM No prison lockup
90 RANDOMIZE USR 39E3
</pre>
 <i>(YS Smash Tips)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
</table></center><P>
